sql_query.sql: SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."updated_at" FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "status_pins" ON "statuses"."id" = "status_pins"."status_id" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status_pins"."account_id" = $1 ORDER BY status_pins.created_at DESC
